---
import Social from "./Social.astro";
---

<footer class="bg-imc">
  <section
    class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-4 sm:p-6 divide-y divide-neutral-200 divide-opacity-40"
  >
    <div
      class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between pb-6"
    >
      <div
        class="w-4/5 sm:w-1/2 text-neutral-200 text-opacity-80 text-center sm:text-left"
      >
        <p class="text-sm mb-4">
          Exerça sua verdadeira liberdade tornando-se sua melhor versão. Sua
          liberdade está em escolher quem você desejar Ser.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-50 text-opacity-100 font-medium">
          Você pode ser a diferença!
        </p>
      </div>
      <Social />
    </div>
    <div class="pt-6 flex flex-col items-center sm:flex-row sm:justify-between">
      <p class="text-sm text-center text-neutral-200 text-opacity-80">
        Copyright &copy; <span id="copyright"></span> | Instituto Medicina Cabalista
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-center text-neutral-200 text-opacity-80">
        <span>by</span>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/andrerousselet"
          target="_blank"
          class="transition hover:text-neutral-200 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-2"
          >Andre Rousselet</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</footer>

<!-- client side js -->
<script>
  const date = document.querySelector("#copyright") as HTMLElement;
  date.textContent = new Date().getFullYear().toString();
</script>
